{
    "title": "Wild Horses",
    "artist": "The Rolling Stones",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Intro]</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Verse 1]</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Childhood living is easy to do</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  The things that you wanted    I bought them for you</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Graceless lady you know who I am</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  You know I can&#x27;t let you    slide through my hands</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Chorus]</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Wild horses    couldn&#x27;t drag me away</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Wild, wild horses    couldn&#x27;t drag me away</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Verse 2]</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  I watched you suffer a dull aching pain</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Now you&#x27;ve decided    to show me the same</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  No sweeping exits or offstage lines</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Could make me feel bitter    or treat you unkind</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Chorus]</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Wild horses    couldn&#x27;t drag me away</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Wild, wild horses    couldn&#x27;t drag me away</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Solo]</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">|F       |C       |F       |C     D |</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">|G   Gsus4 G  |G       |</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Verse 3]</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  I know I dreamed you a sin and a lie</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  I have my freedom    but I don&#x27;t have much time</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Faith has been broken tears must be cried</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Let&#x27;s do some living    after we die</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Chorus]</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Wild horses    couldn&#x27;t drag me away</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Wild, wild horses    we&#x27;ll ride them some day</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Interlude]</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">|Bm      |G       |Bm      |G       |</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">|Am      |C     D |G   Gsus4 G|D       |</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Chorus]</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Bm\">Bm</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Wild horses    couldn&#x27;t drag me away</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am\">Am</span>       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F\">F</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C\">C</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D\">D</span>   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G\">G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">  Wild, wild horses    we&#x27;ll ride them some day</span>\n",
